# {{automobiles}} A set of [[component]]s [[share]]d by several [[vehicle]] models.
# {{context|computing}} A particular type of [[operating system]] or [[environment]] such as a [[database]] or other specific [[software]], and/or a particular type of [[computer]] or [[microprocessor]], used to describe a particular [[environment]] for running other software, or for defining a specific software or hardware environment for discussion purposes.
#: ''That program runs on the X Window System '''platform'''.''
# {{context|politics}} A political [[stance]] on a broad set of issues, which are called [[plank]]s.
# {{travel}} A raised [[structure]] from which [[passenger]]s can [[enter]] or leave a train, metro etc.

